OL,3,CUS author's children 'so scared' of
OL,4,Cher release after she killed her
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,FThe young children of a US author who
OL,8,Fwas found guilty of killing her
OL,9,Fhusband have said they are "afraid" of
OL,10,Ftheir mother ever being released from
OL,11,Fprison.
OL,13,FKouri Richins was convicted in March
OL,14,Fof aggravated murder for lacing her
OL,15,Fhusband Eric Richins' cocktail with
OL,16,Ffive times the lethal dose of fentanyl
OL,17,Fat their home near Park City, Utah, in
OL,18,F2022. She is due to be sentenced today.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778681476
OL,3,CUS author's children 'so scared' of
OL,4,Cher release after she killed her
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,FSoon after his death, she published a
OL,8,Fchildren's book about a son struggling
OL,9,Fwith the grief of their father's death.
OL,11,FIn a memo filed by prosecutors, her
OL,12,Fthree sons, all aged under 14, said
OL,13,Fthey would feel safer if she were
OL,14,Fnever released from prison.
OL,16,F"I'm afraid if she gets out, she will
OL,17,Fcome after me and my brothers, my
OL,18,Fwhole family," said the oldest boy,
OL,19,Fwho is now 13. "I think she would come
OL,20,Fand take us and not do good things to
OL,21,Fus, like hurt us."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778681476
OL,3,CUS author's children 'so scared' of
OL,4,Cher release after she killed her
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,FThe middle child, now 11, said he is
OL,8,Fsad that his dad won't be present for
OL,9,Fmajor milestones. With his mother
OL,10,Fbehind bars, he said he can "live a
OL,11,Fhappy and successful life without fear
OL,12,Fof (her) hurting me or anyone I love."
OL,14,FThe youngest said he would be "so
OL,15,Fscared" if his mother were released.
OL,17,FRichins will be sentenced on
OL,18,FWednesday, and she faces several
OL,19,Fdecades in prison.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
