OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778681476
OL,3,CUS author's children 'so scared' of
OL,4,Cher release after she killed her
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,FProsecutors said Richins, a 35-year-
OL,8,Fold real estate agent with a house-
OL,9,Fflipping business, was millions in
OL,10,Fdebt and planning a future with
OL,11,Fanother man.
OL,13,FShe had opened numerous life insurance
OL,14,Fpolicies on her husband without his
OL,15,Fknowledge and falsely believed she
OL,16,Fwould inherit his estate worth more
OL,17,Fthan $4 million (#2.96 million) after
OL,18,Fhe died.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778681476
OL,3,CUS author's children 'so scared' of
OL,4,Cher release after she killed her
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,FJurors in Park City also found Richins
OL,8,Fguilty of four other felonies,
OL,9,Fincluding attempted murder for trying
OL,10,Fto poison her husband weeks earlier on
OL,11,FValentine's Day with a fentanyl-laced
OL,12,Fsandwich.
OL,14,FHer case captivated true-crime
OL,15,Fenthusiasts when she was arrested in
OL,16,F2023 while promoting her children's
OL,17,Fbook Are You with Me?.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
