CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778681476
OL,3,CUS author's children 'so scared' of
OL,4,Cher release after she killed her
OL,5,Chusband
OL,7,FEric Richins' sister, Amy Richins,
OL,8,Fsaid after the verdict that she was
OL,9,F"just very happy that we got justice
OL,10,Ffor my brother" and could now focus
OL,11,Fsolely on supporting his sons.
OL,13,FThe most serious charge, aggravated
OL,14,Fmurder, is punishable by 25 years to
OL,15,Flife in prison, or a life sentence
OL,16,Fwithout parole. Prosecutors did not
OL,17,Fpush for the death penalty.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
